an attribute set to extend the information","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"IndexedEntity","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" provides easy way to index entities to "},{"code":"CSSearchableIndex","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", while giving ability to customize the attribute set"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I‚Äôve only noted down the intro part of this segment. More details and specific code implementation are missing here."}]}],"name":"Warning","style":"warning"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Entities-and-files","text":"Entities and files"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Transferable-AppEntity","text":"Transferable AppEntity"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Represent an ","type":"text"},{"code":"AppEntity","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in standardized formats like PDF, images, rich text, etc. via ","type":"text"},{"code":"Transferable","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" to pass on custom data to other shortcuts or apps.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Transferable","","extension ActivityStatisticsSummary: Transferable {","    static var transferRepresentation: some TransferRepresentation {","        DataRepresentation(exportedContentType: .rtf) { summary in","            \/\/ Custom method to convert to rich text","            try summary.asRTFData","        }","","        FileRepresentation(exportedContentType: .png) { summary in","            \/\/ Custom method to create PNG file","            SentTransferredFile(try summary.asImageFile)","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The order of transferable representations is important ‚Üí highest to lowest fidelity.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The representation type can be customized in the Shortcuts app via the variable type (tap on variable)."}]},{"type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Restrictions","text":"Restrictions:"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode reads transferable representations at compile time"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"ProxyRepresentation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" only works for references with the "},{"code":"@Property","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Transferable extraction considerations","","struct SomeAppEntity: AppEntity {","    var id: String","","    @Property(title: \"Name\")","    var name: String","","    var description: String { \"\\(id):\\(name)\" }","}","","extension SomeAppEntity: Transferable {","    static var transferRepresentation: some TransferRepresentation {","        ProxyRepresentation(exporting: \\.name) \/\/ Works","        ProxyRepresentation(exporting: \\.description) \/\/ Doesn't work","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}]}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"IntentFile--FileEntity","text":"IntentFile & FileEntity"},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"I‚Äôve skimmed over this section."}]}],"name":"Warning","style":"warning"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Universal-links","text":"Universal links"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Deep-link to app content, allow actions to open URL‚Äôs and make them sharable via "},{"code":"URLRepresentation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URLRepresentableEntity"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"code":"URLRepresentableEnum","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"URLRepresentableIntent"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Universal links","","extension TrailEntity: URLRepresentableEntity {","    static var urlRepresentation: URLRepresentation {","        \"https:\/\/trailsapp.example\/trail\/\\(.id)\/details\"","    }","}","","struct OpenTrailIntent: OpenIntent, URLRepresentableIntent {","    static var title: LocalizedStringResource = \"Open Trail\"","","    static var parameterSummary: some ParameterSummary {","        Summary(\"Open \\(\\.$target)\")","    }","","    @Parameter (title: \"Trail\")","    var target: TrailEntity","}"]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Use any entity "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@Property"},{"type":"text","text":" attribute inside the URL"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Conforming to ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenIntent","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" doesn‚Äôt require a ","type":"text"},{"code":"perform()","type":"codeVoice"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Alternatively, return ","type":"text"},{"code":"OpenURLIntent","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" from perform to open provided URL or the ","type":"text"},{"code":"URLRepresentation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" of an ","type":"text"},{"code":"AppEntity","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":":","type":"text"}]},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ OpensIntent","","func perform() async throws -> some OpensIntent {","    .result(","        opensIntent: OpenURLIntent(","            \"https:\/\/developer.apple.com\"","        )","    )","}"]}],"title":"URL"},{"content":[{"code":["\/\/ OpensIntent","","func perform() async throws -> some OpensIntent {","    let newTrail = TrailEntity(name: name)","    return .result(","        opensIntent: OpenURLIntent(urlRepresentable: newTrail)","    )","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"title":"AppEntity"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Developer-experience","text":"Developer experience"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"UnionValue","text":"UnionValue"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Use the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@UnionValue"},{"text":" macro for parameters that can represented by a set of different types ‚Äì basically an ‚Äúor‚Äù parameter:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["@UnionValue","enum DayPassType {","    case park(ParkEntity)","    case trail(TrailEntity)","}","","struct BuyDayPass: AppIntent {","    \/\/ ‚Ä¶","    @Parameter var passType: DayPassType","    \/\/ ‚Ä¶","    func perform() async throws -> some IntentResult {","        switch passType {","        case let .park(park):","            \/\/ purchase for park","        case let .trail(trail):","            \/\/ purchase for trail","        }","    }","}"]},{"type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Each case must have exactly one value. Non associated values or multiple cases with the same values are not possible."}]}],"name":"Important","style":"important"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Generated-titles","text":"Generated titles"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Xcode 16 doesn‚Äôt require the title for AppEntity properties or AppIntent parameters anymore. It can generate them based on the name of the struct‚Äôs property."}]},{"type":"tabNavigator","tabs":[{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["struct SuggestTrails: AppIntent {","    @Parameter(title: \"Activity\")","    var activity: ActivityStyle","    ","    @Parameter(title: \"Search Radius\")","    var searchRadius: Measurement<UnitLength>?","    ","    @Parameter(title: \"Location\")","    var location: String?","    ","    @Parameter(title: \"Featured Collection\")","    var trailCollection: TrailCollection?","}"]}],"title":"Xcode 15 and before"},{"content":[{"type":"codeListing","code":["struct SuggestTrails: AppIntent {","    @Parameter var activity: ActivityStyle","    @Parameter var searchRadius: Measurement<UnitLength>?","    @Parameter var location: String?","    ","    \/\/ Still possible to explicitly name them","    @Parameter(title: \"Featured Collection\")","    var trailCollection: TrailCollection?","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"title":"Xcode 16+"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Framework-improvements","text":"Framework improvements"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Xcode 16 now allows to have App Intent types in different modules. E.g. putting an ","type":"text"},{"code":"AppEntity","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in a framework and the ","type":"text"},{"code":"AppIntent","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" in the app works now.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"‚ÄúOnly frameworks are supported at this time. Libraries outside of a framework are not.‚Äù","type":"text"}]},{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Written-By","text":"Written By"},{"type":"row","numberOfColumns":5,"columns":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"alexkaessner","type":"image"}]}],"size":1},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":3,"anchor":"Alexander-K%C3%A4%C3%9Fner","text":"Alexander K√§√üner"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"overridingTitle":"Contributed Notes","identifier":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/alexkaessner","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Contributed Notes"}],"isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/github.com\/alexkaessner","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/www.alexkaessner.de\/","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"|","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/x.com\/alexkaessner","isActive":true,"type":"reference"}]}],